returns a list of all the Node objects in the network

<x-color><param>white</param>*****</x-color>* printnodes

prints a representation of all the nodes in the network

<x-color><param>white</param>*****</x-color>* matchindex

returns the node matching a specific index number

<x-color><param>white</param>*****</x-color>* matchprop

returns a list of node objects matching a specific property and value pairing

<x-color><param>white</param>*****</x-color>* createnode

adds a brand new node to the network, and returns it


